<PB N="61" REF="43"> thus replyed: My love let me de&s;ire you to be merry, for to morrow morning, you &s;hall be re|venged and my &s;elf al&s;o of the outrages that have bin done to us, whereupon the Empre&s;s was merry, and contented.</P>
