<FIGDESC>top left: representation of a male figure and female figure standing in a room; top right: representation of two male figures and a female figure seated at a table, with two female figures standing nearby; middle left: representation of two male figures standing, with two male figures kneeling nearby; middle right: representation of four male figures standing in a room; bottom left: representation of two male figures taking hold of a male figure, nearby a fire; bottom right: representation of two male figures, one with a sword cutting the head off another male figure</FIGDESC>
</FIGURE>
